{"title":"社员歌唱红太阳（两首）","authors":["殷光兰"],"dates":[{"year":1968,"month":5,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员歌唱红太阳（两首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安徽省肥东县店埠公社社员　殷光兰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高山青松最坚强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社庄稼最兴旺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗招展歌更多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放声歌唱红太阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席就是红太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金光闪闪万道光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当代列宁举红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界人民有方向。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“大海航行靠舵手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干革命靠毛泽东思想。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有咱们毛主席掌大舵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀山火海全敢闯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席就是红太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照得咱们心里亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照得帝、修、反完了蛋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照得红旗天下扬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦苗青青菜花黄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色宝书带身上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"埂边插上语录牌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田里掀起千层浪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“抓革命，促生产”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席教导记心上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人争当老愚公，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里大地穿新装。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"誓夺革命、生产双胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜报寄给红太阳。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}